%%{init: {'theme':'base'}}%%
graph TD
    Start([System Start]) --> Login{User Login}
    
    %% Student Path
    Login -->|Student| StudentDash[Student Dashboard]
    StudentDash --> ViewCourses[View Enrolled Courses]
    ViewCourses --> SelectCourse[Select Course]
    SelectCourse --> ViewQuizzes[View Available Quizzes]
    ViewQuizzes --> CheckDeadline{Quiz Deadline<br/>Passed?}
    
    CheckDeadline -->|Yes| DeadlineMsg[Show: Quiz Expired]
    DeadlineMsg --> ViewQuizzes
    
    CheckDeadline -->|No| CheckAttempts{Max Attempts<br/>Reached?}
    CheckAttempts -->|Yes| AttemptsMsg[Show: No Attempts Left]
    AttemptsMsg --> ViewQuizzes
    
    CheckAttempts -->|No| StartQuiz[Start Quiz Attempt]
    StartQuiz --> CreateAttempt[Create Attempt Record]
    CreateAttempt --> DisplayQuiz[Display Quiz Questions]
    DisplayQuiz --> AnswerQuestions[Student Answers Questions]
    AnswerQuestions --> SubmitQuiz[Submit Attempt]
    SubmitQuiz --> AutoGradeMCQ{Any MCQ<br/>Questions?}
    
    AutoGradeMCQ -->|Yes| GradeMCQs[Auto-grade MCQs]
    AutoGradeMCQs --> CheckWritten{Has Written<br/>Questions?}
    
    AutoGradeMCQ -->|No| CheckWritten
    
    CheckWritten -->|Yes| MarkPending[Mark Attempt as Pending]
    MarkPending --> ShowScore[Show MCQ Score Only]
    ShowScore --> PendingMsg[Show: Pending Manual Grading]
    
    CheckWritten -->|No| CalcFinalScore[Calculate Final Score]
    CalcFinalScore --> MarkGraded[Mark Attempt as Graded]
    MarkGraded --> UpdateXP[Update Student XP]
    UpdateXP --> CheckBadges{Badge<br/>Conditions<br/>Met?}
    
    CheckBadges -->|Yes| UnlockBadges[Unlock Badges]
    CheckBadges -->|No| CheckPowerUps
    UnlockBadges --> CheckPowerUps{PowerUp<br/>Thresholds<br/>Met?}
    
    CheckPowerUps -->|Yes| UnlockPowerUps[Unlock PowerUps]
    CheckPowerUps -->|No| ShowResult
    UnlockPowerUps --> ShowResult[Show Final Score & Unlocked Items]
    ShowResult --> ViewLeaderboard{View<br/>Leaderboard?}
    
    ViewLeaderboard -->|Yes| FetchLeaderboard[Fetch Latest Attempts<br/>Per Student]
    FetchLeaderboard --> SortLeaderboard[Sort by Score then Speed]
    SortLeaderboard --> DisplayLB[Display Ranked Leaderboard]
    DisplayLB --> StudentEnd([Student Done])
    
    ViewLeaderboard -->|No| StudentEnd
    PendingMsg --> StudentEnd
    ShowScore --> ViewLeaderboard
    
    %% Instructor Path
    Login -->|Instructor| InstDash[Instructor Dashboard]
    InstDash --> InstChoice{Action?}
    
    InstChoice -->|Create Quiz| CreateQuiz[Create New Quiz]
    CreateQuiz --> AddQuestions[Add Questions<br/>MCQ & Written]
    AddQuestions --> SetDeadline[Set Deadline & Max Attempts]
    SetDeadline --> PublishQuiz[Publish Quiz to Sections]
    PublishQuiz --> AnalyticsView{View?}
    
    InstChoice -->|View Analytics| AnalyticsView
    AnalyticsView -->|Yes| FetchAnalytics[Fetch Quiz Attempts<br/>for Section]
    FetchAnalytics --> CalcAnalytics[Calculate Avg Score<br/>& Struggled Quiz]
    CalcAnalytics --> DisplayAnalytics[Display Analytics Dashboard]
    DisplayAnalytics --> AnalyticsEnd([Analytics Done])
    
    AnalyticsView -->|No, Back| InstDash
    PublishQuiz --> InstDash
    
    InstChoice -->|Grade Pending| ViewPending[View Pending Quizzes]
    ViewPending --> FetchPending[Fetch Ungraded Attempts<br/>with Written Q's]
    FetchPending --> ListPending[Display Pending List]
    ListPending --> SelectAttempt[Select Attempt to Grade]
    SelectAttempt --> FetchAttemptDetails[Fetch Attempt Details<br/>& Student Answers]
    FetchAttemptDetails --> DisplayAnswers[Display Written Answers]
    DisplayAnswers --> EnterScores[Instructor Enters Scores<br/>for Written Answers]
    EnterScores --> SaveGrades[Save Grades]
    SaveGrades --> RecalcScore[Recalculate Total Score<br/>MCQ + Written]
    RecalcScore --> MarkGradedFinal[Mark Attempt as Graded]
    MarkGradedFinal --> CalcXPFinal[Calculate New XP<br/>for Student]
    CalcXPFinal --> CheckBadgesFinal{Badge<br/>Conditions<br/>Met?}
    
    CheckBadgesFinal -->|Yes| UnlockBadgesFinal[Unlock Badges<br/>for Student]
    CheckBadgesFinal -->|No| CheckPowerUpsFinal
    UnlockBadgesFinal --> CheckPowerUpsFinal{PowerUp<br/>Thresholds<br/>Met?}
    
    CheckPowerUpsFinal -->|Yes| UnlockPowerUpsFinal[Unlock PowerUps<br/>for Student]
    CheckPowerUpsFinal -->|No| ConfirmGrade
    UnlockPowerUpsFinal --> ConfirmGrade[Show Grading Complete<br/>& Unlocked Items]
    ConfirmGrade --> MoreGrading{More<br/>Attempts?}
    
    MoreGrading -->|Yes| ListPending
    MoreGrading -->|No| InstEnd([Instructor Done])
    
    InstChoice -->|View Leaderboard| ViewInstLB[View Instructor Leaderboard]
    ViewInstLB --> FetchInstLB[Fetch Graded Attempts<br/>for Section]
    FetchInstLB --> KeepLatest[Keep Latest Attempt<br/>Per Student Per Quiz]
    KeepLatest --> CalcAvgScore[Calculate Average Score<br/>Across Quizzes]
    CalcAvgScore --> SortInstLB[Sort by Avg Score]
    SortInstLB --> DisplayInstLB[Display Ranked Students]
    DisplayInstLB --> InstEnd
    
    AnalyticsEnd --> InstDash
    
    %% System Notifications
    MarkGradedFinal -.->|Notify| Notify["Send Notification<br/>Student: Attempt Graded!"]
    Notify -.-> StudentEnd
